set -Eeuo pipefail

cat <<EOF
Usage: $0 <command>

The following commands are supported:

de help:                  This help page.

de init:                  Initialize the development environment.

de collect-garbage:       Garbage collect the development environment.

de format                 Run platform-independaent formatters, linters and the
                          3rd party license checker.

de license-check:         Ensures that usage of 3rd party software licenses are
                          acknowledged and the license type is whitelisted.

de vendor:                Vendors a GitLab mirror as an submodule of the project.

EOF


